import React, { Fragment } from "react"
import StoneWhaleBeach from "./StoneWhaleBeach"
import {
  Wrap,
  Mask,
  Container,
  Left,
  Right,
  Text,
  Paragrah,
  NumberText,
  Number,
  Title,
  Column,
} from "../styles"

class NoDistance extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Wrap>
          <Mask>
            <Container>
              <Left />
              <Right>
                <Text>No Distance is Too Far</Text>
                <Paragrah>
                  Whether you are travelling to the other side of the globe or
                  interstate, our travel agency will provide an ideal travel
                  experience.
                </Paragrah>
              </Right>
            </Container>
            <NumberText>
              <Column>
                <Number>102</Number>
                <Title>Destinations</Title>
              </Column>
              <Column>
                <Number>500</Number>
                <Title>Packages</Title>
              </Column>
              <Column>
                <Number>75</Number>
                <Title>Staff members</Title>
              </Column>
              <Column>
                <Number>20</Number>
                <Title>Years of Experiences</Title>
              </Column>
            </NumberText>
          </Mask>
        </Wrap>
        <StoneWhaleBeach />
      </>
    )
  }
}

export default NoDistance
